</tbody></table></div>
<div class="p text-right font-secondary"><a href="table/Tab1/" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in a new tab</a></div></section><p id="Par9">Finally, as an additional comparative measure, the frequency with which individual categories listed in the ABII TCO were tested was identified based on the number of allotted exam questions and compared against imaging informatics fellowship director appraisal of topic importance [<a href="#CR9" class="usa-link" aria-describedby="CR9">9</a>].</p></section><section id="Sec3"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">Results</h2>
<p id="Par10">From the eight fellowship directors contacted, five completed the survey corresponding to a 63% response rate. The institutions were all located along the East Coast and all trained exclusively MD/DO candidates. Table <a href="#Tab2" class="usa-link">2</a> shows the breakdown of the original 29 broad curriculum topics into 114 sub-topics.</p>
<section class="tw xbox font-sm" id="Tab2"><h3 class="obj_head">Table 2.</h3>
